**Springer Nature Editor of Distinction Award 2025** honors Palanichamy Naveen. 

Springer Nature honors exceptional editors, whose dedication to their journals and research communities is truly inspiring.

Palanichamy Naveen, had been selected to receive the following awards for his outstanding contributions to the Nature - Scientific Reports:

1) The Editorial Contribution Award. This award recognizes his meticulous assessment of submissions and rigorous management of the peer review process, safeguarding the scientific accuracy of the published record.

2) The Author Service Award. This award recognizes his exceptional service in improving the author experience and ensuring the peer review process is efficient, constructive, and fair.
